        <Parent_String>mechanical drawings (building systems drawings) [300034557], architectural drawings (visual works) [300034787], drawings by subject type [300034783], drawings (visual works) [300033973], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
